<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The documentation implies that the following is possible:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$filter = new Zend_Filter_Encrypt(array(
    'adapter' =&gt; 'openssl',
    'private' =&gt; '/path/to/mykey/private.pem'
));
</code></pre>

<p>The problem is that all arguments handed to the adapter, will be used as public key.</p>

